teristics and even removing those considered essential ones, creating thus a figure that would give a new meaning to the term \"superfluous man\".", "Data de Publicação": "2016-05-16", "url": "http://www.teses.usp.br/teses/disponiveis/8/8155/tde-16052016-144256/pt-br.php"}
